60\" href=\"http://www.bbc.co.uk/ethics/guide/\">Ethics guide</a>\r\n\r\n\t\t</h3>\r\n\r\n\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Debates surrounding ethical issues in everyday life \t\r\n\t\t\t\t  <span id=\"dna-comment-count___CPS__19603334\" class=\"gvl3-icon gvl3-icon-comment comment-count\"></span></p>\r\n\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</li>\r\n\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t<li class=\"no-image\">\r\n\r\n\t\t\t\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\t\r\n\r\n\r\n\t\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h3 class=\" feature-header\">\r\n\t<a class=\"story\" rel=\"published-1349274624132\" href=\"http://www.bbc.co.uk/religion/greatbritishfaith/\">Faith Map</a>\r\n\r\n\t\t</h3>\r\n\r\n\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Religion in the UK illustrated with an interactive map \t\r\n\t\t\t\t  <span id=\"dna-comment-count___CPS__19816472\" class=\"gvl3-icon gvl3-icon-comment comment-count\"></span></p>\r\n\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</li>\r\n\t\r\n\t \r\n\t\r\n\t\r\n\r\n\r\n   </ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<script type=\"text/javascript\">$render(\"container-features-and-analysis\",\"genre-promotion\");</script> \r\n\r\n\t       \t         <div id=\"iplayer-promotion\" class=\"include-only programmes-promotion\">\r\n    \t\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\t\t     <div class=\"hyperpuff\">\r\n\t       \t             \t\t  \t\t    \t\r\n    \t\t    \t\t    \t\t  \t\t  \r\n\r\n<div id=\"container-programme-promotion\" class=\"container-programme-promotion\">\r\n\t\t\t<h2 class=\"programmes-header\">Programmes</h2>\r\n\t\t\r\n\t\r\n\t\t<a class=\"iplayer-branding\" href=\"http://www.bbc.co.uk/iplayer/\">BBC iPlayer</a>\r\n\t\r\n\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n<ul class=\"programme-breakout\">\r\n\t\r\n\t\r\n\t\t\t\r\n\t<li class=\"first-child large-image\">\t\t\r\n\t\t\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\t\r\n\r\n\r\n\t\t\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h3 class=\" programme-header\">\r\n\t<a class=\"story\" rel=\"published-1389368615662\" href=\"http://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043bpqb\"><img src=\"http://news.bbcimg.co.uk/media/images/72208000/jpg/_72208423_b03pmmrj.jpg\" alt=\"The Big Questions\" />Big Ques